text.tspan: • Normal sudoku: Fill every row, coloumn and marked 3×3 box
with the digits 1 to 9 once each.
• Classic Kropki: Cells connected by a black dot have a ratio of 1:2.
• XVXV: Cells connected by a V sum to either 5 or 15;
cells connected by a X sum to either 10 or 15.
